1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,000
IntentProof keeps agent actions inside local policy and user-held signing control.

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:15,000
Unsafe actions are blocked before a wallet is asked to sign.

3
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:25,000
Approved actions create SHA-256-linked receipts that can be exported as evidence.

4
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:34,000
At the Devnet signing boundary, only the operator's Phantom wallet can authorize the transaction.
